We can add this within the header section,

00:04:52.030 --> 00:04:54.965
but just after the nav element.

00:04:54.965 --> 00:04:57.120
The text of "Hi, I'm Chris",

00:04:57.120 --> 00:04:59.805
I'm going to add in a level one heading.

00:04:59.805 --> 00:05:06.095
HTML provides us with headings we can use from Level 1 through to Level 6.

00:05:06.095 --> 00:05:11.160
Level 1 is going to be the biggest and also the most important.

00:05:11.160 --> 00:05:16.160
The size and importance drops down as the number gets higher.

00:05:16.160 --> 00:05:19.560
Add the text for your project,

00:05:20.150 --> 00:05:23.780
and then below this we have the regular text.

00:05:23.780 --> 00:05:26.540
We add regular text in the p element,

00:05:26.540 --> 00:05:28.660
