and this is going to be our vertical text.

00:05:49.835 --> 00:05:54.960
The vertical text though is not created using HTML.

00:05:54.960 --> 00:05:59.445
The HTML is simply there to add the content to our page.

00:05:59.445 --> 00:06:03.040
We're going to add this using a Level 3 heading.

00:06:03.040 --> 00:06:08.095
This will appear in the browser at the moment just as a regular horizontal text,

00:06:08.095 --> 00:06:11.720
